.IX Title "FVWM-MENU-DIRECTORY 1"
.TH FVWM-MENU-DIRECTORY 1 "2003-03-15" "perl v5.8.0" "FVWM Utilities"
.SH "NAME"
fvwm\-menu\-directory \- builds a directory browsing menu for FVWM
.SH "SYNOPSIS"
.IX Header "SYNOPSIS"
